          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die ausgeglichenen Kräfte,

          </description>

            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre les forces

qui leur font toujours le séjour.</string>
          </description>

            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostram as forças equilibradas

          </description>
